Actress Tonto Dike has offered insights into what she would have done to Will Smith if she were Chris Rock. American actor Will Smith slapped Chris Rock on the stage of the OSCARS award ceremony on Sunday evening after the latter made a joke on his wife’s health condition. The development created frenzy with Smith apologizing to Chris Rock and the Academy for his “inexcusable” action. But Tonto Dikeh said if she were Chris Rock, she would have reciprocated the unwelcome gesture.   Jubilation as Mr Ibu leaves hospital     Comedian MC Morris yanks off Portable from show     Sacked promoter cuts ties with Portable   She tweeted: “I felt it when @willsmith said love can make you do crazy things. I will do worse for my child. “I’m scared of how far I will protect my POTE (wingman/child) “I get @willsmith vulnerability but also I respect @chrisrock fo his professionalism because if it were me, It’s a show over. Everyone must go home.”